V<div dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;" trbidi="on"><div style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;">&nbsp;<b>By PNV Ram</b>  </div><div class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;"><br />\u000a</div><div class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;">An early highlight of last year\u2019s Chennai music season was the mellow nayanam purveyed by Vyasarpadi Kothandaraman at the Music Academy on the first morning of the festival there. Eagerly scanning the announcements for this season, I found that Kothandaraman had a record number of concert engagements for this season\u2014exactly zero. I consider him one of the best nagaswaram vidwans around today and it made me sad to note his absence from the list of performers, but I had yet another shock awaiting me. The brilliant maestro Injikkudi EM Subramaniam has only one performance this season, unless I am missing out on concerts announced elsewhere.</div><div class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;"><br />\u000a</div><div class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;">Anyone who has heard these wonderful instrumentalists will know that they represent the best of an almost bygone tradition of temple music, which they have striven to preserve intact against all odds, with their would-be successors moving to other, securer occupations, and audiences dwindling more rapidly than sparrows from our environment.</div><div class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;"><br />\u000a</div><div class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; margin: 3pt 0in; text-align: justify;">Sruti and The Music Forum, Chennai, quickly moved in and invited Kothandaraman to offer a demonstration of the manodharma relating to Todi raga in all its grandeur during the Lec-Dem Mela being co-presented by them during 10-12 December 2011 at the Arkay Convention Centre on Royapettah High Road, near Luz Corner. Please see the whole programme below.</div><div align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; margin: 3pt 0in; text-align: center;"><br />\u000a<b>The Music Forum in association with SRUTI magazine presents</b></div><div align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; margin: 3pt 0in; text-align: center;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16pt;">&nbsp; </span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">LEC DEM MELA \u2013 MANODHARMA IN CARNATIC MUSIC</b></div><div style="-moz-border-bottom-colors: none; -moz-border-image: none; -moz-border-left-colors: none; -moz-border-right-colors: none; -moz-border-top-colors: none; border-color: -moz-use-text-color -moz-use-text-color windowtext; border-style: none none solid; border-width: medium medium 0.75pt; font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; padding: 0in 0in 1pt;"><div align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="border: none; margin-bottom: 3.0pt; margin-left: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-top: 3.0pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .75pt; mso-padding-alt: 0in 0in 1.0pt 0in; padding: 0in; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Venue: Arkay Convention Center, Luz, Chennai-4. Ph. 9381023173/ 9444123645</span></div></div><div align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; margin: 3pt 0in; text-align: center;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">PROGRAMME SCHEDULE</b></div><div align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; margin: 3pt 0in; text-align: center;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">10<sup>th</sup> Dec 2011s</b></div><div class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; margin: 3pt 0in;">9 am to 10 am <br />\u000aRaga Kharaharapriya and its janya ragas \u2013 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Sri O.S. Thyagarajan</div><div style="-moz-border-bottom-colors: none; -moz-border-image: none; -moz-border-left-colors: none; -moz-border-right-colors: none; -moz-border-top-colors: none; border-color: -moz-use-text-color -moz-use-text-color windowtext; border-style: none none solid; border-width: medium medium 0.75pt; font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; padding: 0in 0in 1pt;"><div class="MsoNormal" style="border: none; margin-bottom: 3.0pt; margin-left: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-top: 3.0pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .75pt; mso-padding-alt: 0in 0in 1.0pt 0in; padding: 0in;">10.15 am to 11.15 am <br />\u000aDifferences in approach to niraval and swara singing \u2013 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Chitraveena Sri. N. Ravikiran</div><div class="MsoNormal" style="border: none; margin-bottom: 3.0pt; margin-left: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-top: 3.0pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .75pt; mso-padding-alt: 0in 0in 1.0pt 0in; padding: 0in;">11.30 am to 1.00 pm <br />\u000aManodharma excellence in yester year musicians \u2013 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Dr. Radha Bhaskar</div></div><div align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; margin: 3pt 0in; text-align: center;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">11<sup>th</sup> Dec 2011</b></div><div class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; margin: 3pt 0in;">9.00 am to 9.45 am <br />\u000aVerbal and aesthetic excellence in the lyrics of Tyagaraja and Muthuswamy Dikshitar\u2019s compositions &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Prof. S. R. Janakiraman</div><div class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; margin: 3pt 0in;">10.00 am to 11.30 am <br />\u000aBhakti poets and Indian music &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Dr. Gowri Ramnarayan</div><div style="-moz-border-bottom-colors: none; -moz-border-image: none; -moz-border-left-colors: none; -moz-border-right-colors: none; -moz-border-top-colors: none; border-color: -moz-use-text-color -moz-use-text-color windowtext; border-style: none none solid; border-width: medium medium 0.75pt; font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; padding: 0in 0in 1pt;"><div class="MsoNormal" style="border: none; margin-bottom: 3.0pt; margin-left: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-top: 3.0pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .75pt; mso-padding-alt: 0in 0in 1.0pt 0in; padding: 0in;">11.30am to 12.30 pm <br />\u000aScope of manodharma in music for dance&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Dr. Padma Subrahmanyam and Dr. Gayatri Kannan</div><div class="MsoNormal" style="border: none; margin-bottom: 3.0pt; margin-left: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-top: 3.0pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .75pt; mso-padding-alt: 0in 0in 1.0pt 0in; padding: 0in; text-align: justify;"><br />\u000a</div></div><div class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; margin: 3pt 0in 3pt 2in; text-indent: 0.5in;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">12<sup>th</sup> Dec 2011</b></div><div class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; margin: 3pt 0in;">8.30 to 9.30 a.m. <br />\u000aManodharma in Todi raga&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Vyasarpadi Kothandaraman (nagaswaram)</div><div class="MsoBodyText" style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; margin: 3pt 0in;">9.30 to 10.30 a.m.  <br />\u000aThe raga Harikhamboji and its janya ragas &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Kalaimamani Dr. Sunder </div><div class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; margin: 3pt 0in; text-align: justify;">10.45 to 11.30 a.m.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\u000aManodharma aspects in tani avartanam&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Karaikudi Sri. Mani</div><div style="-moz-border-bottom-colors: none; -moz-border-image: none; -moz-border-left-colors: none; -moz-border-right-colors: none; -moz-border-top-colors: none; border-color: -moz-use-text-color -moz-use-text-color windowtext; border-style: none none solid; border-width: medium medium 0.75pt; font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; padding: 0in 0in 1pt;"><div class="MsoNormal" style="border: none; margin-bottom: 3.0pt; margin-left: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-top: 3.0pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .75pt; mso-padding-alt: 0in 0in 1.0pt 0in; padding: 0in;">11.45 a.m. to 12.30 pm <br />\u000aVarious aspects of tanam &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Sri. P. Vasanthkumar - Veena </div><div class="MsoNormal" style="border: none; margin-bottom: 3.0pt; margin-left: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-top: 3.0pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .75pt; mso-padding-alt: 0in 0in 1.0pt 0in; padding: 0in; text-align: justify;"><br />\u000a</div></div><div align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; margin: 3pt 0in; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 13pt;">ADMISSION FREE BUT BY PRIOR REGISTRATION ONLY</span></div><div align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; margin: 3pt 0in; text-align: center;">For registrations contact \u2013 9381023173/ 9444123645<span style="font-size: 9pt;"></span></div><span style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;">  </span><span style="font-family: Georgia,&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 12pt;">For online registrations contact: <a href="mailto:musicforum.chennai@gmail.com">musicforum.chennai@gmail.com</a></span></div>
